---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CASL Compliance | 3D3D" description="How 3D3D complies with Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation (CASL)." activePath="/casl">

  <div class="pt-8 pb-12">
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{label: 'Home', href: '/'}, {label: 'Legal'}, {label: 'CASL Compliance'}]} />
      <p class="font-display text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mt-2 mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">CASL Compliance</h1>
      <p class="font-display text-xs mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text-muted);">Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation</p>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Our Commitment</h2>
          <p>3D3D Atlantic Cooperative complies fully with Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation (CASL). We only send commercial electronic messages to recipients who have given express or implied consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Express Consent</h2>
          <p>We obtain express consent through opt-in checkboxes on our order forms, maker applications, and newsletter signup. We never pre-check consent boxes. Consent records (date, source, method) are stored securely.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Implied Consent</h2>
          <p>Implied consent applies for 24 months after a purchase or 6 months after an inquiry. After this period, we require express consent to continue sending commercial messages.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Unsubscribe</h2>
          <p>Every commercial email includes a clear, functional unsubscribe mechanism. Unsubscribe requests are processed within 10 business days (typically within hours). You can also email <a href="mailto:info@3d3d.ca" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-teal-primary);">info@3d3d.ca</a> to unsubscribe.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Identification</h2>
          <p>All commercial emails clearly identify 3D3D Atlantic Cooperative as the sender, include our physical mailing address (Moncton, NB), and provide contact information.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-base font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-text-primary);">Transactional Messages</h2>
          <p>Order confirmations, shipping notifications, and account-related messages are transactional and exempt from CASL consent requirements. These are sent only in relation to an existing transaction or account.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
